{"tid":1044053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為兩公司否認美國刑事指控！","createTime":"2019-03-02T15:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T01:05:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d754e121b5764af54dd30c5a6f9beb7d2aa39e9","tid":1044053,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"Roy<br />\nMar 01, 2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.android-hk.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/tmobile-tappy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Ftmobile-tappy.jpg&h=be939956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早於一月份的時候，美國司法部就 2012 至 2014 年期間，華為以非法的手段偷取 T-Mobile 商業機密資料，對華為作出起訴。現在，司法部表示華為兩家公司 Huawei Device Co. Ltd. 及 Huawei Device USA Inc 已否認相關指控。<br />\n據了解，華為曾偷取 T-Mobile 一部用來測試機，名為 Tappy 機械人的相關資料。消息指，T-Mobile 曾表示有安全攝影鏡頭，拍攝到一名華為員工將 Tappy 機械人的手臂拆除，並放進自己的電腦袋中帶走。結果於 2012 至 2013 年間，華為利用 Tappy 的技術設計相關的軟件及自己的機械人工具。"},{"pid":"6f08365f5d0929a0349a9faeaed926ba5b7ac1f8","tid":1044053,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.android-hk.com/news/huawei-units-plead-not-guilty-to-criminal-charges-android-hk-1319/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fnews%2Fhuawei-units-plead-not-guilty-to-criminal-charges-android-hk-1319%2F&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyENAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=49fa79f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.android-hk.com/news/huawei-units-plead-not-guilty-to-criminal-charges-android-hk-1319/</a>"},{"pid":"5fcff7e41c186d7135e4e63e15b1b043a0e9ef44","tid":1044053,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:00:49.000Z","msg":"死不認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737c2aa6db01946657d0233d2b5e4e065905ec79","tid":1044053,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T1